{"title_page": "Ningbo", "text_new": "{{other uses}}\n{{redirect|Liampo|the nearby settlement referred to by this name by the Portuguese in the 16th century|Shuangyu}}\n\n<!-- Infobox begins -->\n{{stack|{{Infobox settlement\n| name                   = {{raise|0.2em|Ningbo}}\n| official_name          = <!-- Official name in English if different from 'name' -->\n| native_name            = {{lower|0.1em|{{nobold|{{lang|zh-hans|\u5b81\u6ce2\u5e02}}}}}}\n| other_name             = Ning-po, Nhingpo \n| settlement_type        = [[Prefecture-level city|Prefecture-level]] & [[Sub-provincial city]]\n| image_skyline          = {{multiple image\n| border                 = infobox\n| total_width            = 280\n| image_style            = border:1;\n| perrow                 = 1/2/2/\n| image1                 = Ningbo South Business District 24-09-2018.jpg\n| image2                 = Ningbo - Tianyi Pavilion Museum 04.jpg\n| image3                 = Yinzhou District Government of Ningbo 24-09-2018.jpg\n| image4                 = Dongqian_lake.jpg\n| image5                 = Tianfeng Pagoda in Ningbo.jpg\n}}\n| image_caption          = '''Clockwise:''' South Business District, [[Yinzhou District, Ningbo|Yinzhou District Government of Ningbo]], Tianfeng Pagoda, [[Dongqian Lake]], [[Tianyi Ge|Tianyi Pavilion]] Museum \n| image_flag             =\n| image_seal             =\n| image_shield           =\n| nickname               =\n| motto                  =\n| image_map              = {{maplink|frame=yes|plain=yes|type=shape|stroke-width=2|stroke-color=#000000|zoom=7|frame-lat=29.59|frame-long=121.55}}\n| image_map1             = ChinaZhejiangNingbo.png\n| map_caption1           = Ningbo City in Zhejiang\n| pushpin_map            = China\n| pushpin_label_position = right\n| pushpin_map_caption    = Location in China\n| coor_pinpoint = [[Tianyi Square]]\n| coordinates            = {{coord|29.869|N|121.554|E|format=dms|type:adm2nd_region:CN-33_source:Gaode|display=it}}\n| subdivision_